metadata.name: The Beasts of No Nation 001
metadata.description:
001

The Beasts Of No Nation is a series of unique handcrafted collectibles within the decentralized digital landscape.

Each collectible consists of a creature juxtaposed to a meticulous environment, giving them a one of a kind identity.

More variety of beasts will be progressively added to the collection while each species will only be created once to ensure its rarity.
